<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id44fcebe5-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id44fcebe6-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 1393, added <ref href="/us/pl/95/600/tVI/s601/a">Pub. L. 95–600, title VI, § 601(a)</ref>, <date date="1978-11-06">Nov. 6, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/2894">92 Stat. 2894</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/96/595/s3/a/5">Pub. L. 96–595, § 3(a)(5)</ref>, (6), (8), <date date="1980-12-24">Dec. 24, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3465">94 Stat. 3465</ref>, related to taxation of general stock ownership corporation taxable income to shareholders, prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/99/514/tXIII/s1303/a">Pub. L. 99–514, title XIII, § 1303(a)</ref>, <date date="1986-10-22">Oct. 22, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/2658">100 Stat. 2658</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
